data.text:
The January transfers season brings new cards to FIFA 13 Ultimate Team. Know them.

The new FUT 13 cards of January transfers

At January transfers season many players find a new direction for their career.

In order to keep the game updated, the EA moves to FIFA 13 Ultimate Team what is happening in the transfer market.

The FUT 13 cards of players that are transferred start being released with the new club. The cards with the old club are no longer released in packs, but those which are already in circulation remain. That is, the same player can have cards from two different clubs.

The new cards have the particularity to stir up the FIFA 13 Ultimate Team market. The great interest that they may have is to allow more combinations of teams without damaging the chemistry.
